AssociateProfile.name: AssociateProfile
AssociateProfile.description: Grants permission to associates a Profile to the customer VPC

AssociateResourceToProfile.name: AssociateResourceToProfile
AssociateResourceToProfile.description: Grants permission to associates a resource, such as DNS Firewall rule group, private hosted zone, resolver rule, etc. to a specified Profile

CreateProfile.name: CreateProfile
CreateProfile.description: Grants permission to create a new Profile resource

DeleteProfile.name: DeleteProfile
DeleteProfile.description: Grants permission to delete a Profile specified by the ProfileId

DisassociateProfile.name: DisassociateProfile
DisassociateProfile.description: Grants permission to delete an association between a customer VPC and the specified Profile

DisassociateResourceFromProfile.name: DisassociateResourceFromProfile
DisassociateResourceFromProfile.description: Grants permission to delete the asoociation between the resource. such as DNS Firewall rule group, private hosted zone, resolver rule, etc. and the specified Profile

GetProfile.name: GetProfile
GetProfile.description: Grants permission to get a Profile

GetProfileAssociation.name: GetProfileAssociation
GetProfileAssociation.description: Grants permission to get a Profile to a VPC association specified by the Profile association ID

GetProfilePolicy.name: GetProfilePolicy
GetProfilePolicy.description: Grants permission to read the RAM access control policy for a Profile

GetProfileResourceAssociation.name: GetProfileResourceAssociation
GetProfileResourceAssociation.description: Grants permission to get a Profile resource association based on the ProfileResourceAssociationId

ListProfileAssociations.name: ListProfileAssociations
ListProfileAssociations.description: Grants permission to list all VPCs the specified Profile is associated to

ListProfileResourceAssociations.name: ListProfileResourceAssociations
ListProfileResourceAssociations.description: Grants permission to list all the associations between the resources, such as DNS Firewall rule groups, private hosted zones, resolver rules, etc. for the given Profile ID

ListProfiles.name: ListProfiles
ListProfiles.description: Grants permission to list all the Profiles created by, and shared to the customer

ListTagsForResource.name: ListTagsForResource
ListTagsForResource.description: Grants permission to list all tags associated with the resource

PutProfilePolicy.name: PutProfilePolicy
PutProfilePolicy.description: Grants permission to define the RAM access control policy for a Profile

TagResource.name: TagResource
TagResource.description: Grants permission to add a tag to the given resource

UntagResource.name: UntagResource
UntagResource.description: Grants permission to delete a tag from the given resource

UpdateProfileResourceAssociation.name: UpdateProfileResourceAssociation
UpdateProfileResourceAssociation.description: Grants permission to update the Profile resource association name or the resource properties or both, if both name and resource properties are null, the api returns the existing Profile resource association
